        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/publications/nasal-carcinoma-and-occupational-exposure-to-wood-dust-iiac-report">Nasal carcinoma and occupational exposure to wood dust: IIAC report</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
